        <h1>Warrior Cats Favorite Picker</h1>
        <p>As you start and continue on, groups of characters from Warrior Cats will appear on the screen. Pick one or more of these characters and press the "Pick" button. If there are none, feel free to press the "Pass" button! Soon enough your favourite kitties will appear under the "Found Favourites" text. Enjoy!</p>
        <p>Realistically (and hopefully), this picker is pretty accurate, provided you pick consistently - you'll correctly get your second favorite second, even if it's pitted against your absolute favorite early on, for instance. You can also reorder your favorites after you've found them if you want.</p>
        <p>
            Feel free to include or exclude certain books / arcs based on what you have or haven't read! I recommend removing Field Guides if you want to get through this faster and Newly Released Books if you want to avoid possible spoilers.
        </p>
        <p>
            <li><b>Field Guides</b> include Code of the Clans, Secrets of the Clans, The Ultimate Guide, etc.</li>
            <li><b>Prequels</b> include Bluestar's Prophecy, Cloudstar's Journey, Mapleshade's Vengenance and basically any other book that takes place <i>before</i> TPB.</li>
            <li><b>Modern SkyClan Books</b> include Firestar's Quest, SkyClan's Destiny, Hawkwing's Journey, etc.</li>
            <li><b>Newly Released Books</b> include books that have been released in the past 3 months. <sub>currently this includes Chasing Shadows.</sub></li>
        </p>
        <p>
            Art by <a href="https://cloudtail.tumblr.com/">Ursiday,</a>
            <a href="https://warriorsproject.tumblr.com/">Nifty Senpai,</a>
            <a href="https://eggfeather.tumblr.com/">Eggfeather,</a>
            <a href="https://keblestone.tumblr.com/">Keblestone</a> &
            <a href="https://velo-cats.tumblr.com/">Velociras!</a>
        </p>
        <p>
            Original source code by <a href="https://twitter.com/antialiasis">antialiasis</a>
            with instructions <a href="https://github.com/antialiasis/favorite-picker">here,</a>
            based off of the <a href="https://www.dragonflycave.com/favorite.html">Favorite Pokemon Picker!</a>
        </p>
